--font-family-vault.light: Arlrdbd, "Source Han Sans", "Noto Sans CJK", "Source Sans Pro"

background-image.light: repeating-linear-gradient( 45deg, hsla(0, 0%, 100%, 0.3), hsla(0, 0%, 100%, 0.3) 20px, transparent 0, transparent 60px ), repeating-linear-gradient( -45deg, hsla(0, 0%, 100%, 0.3), hsla(0, 0%, 100%, 0.3) 20px, transparent 0, transparent 60px )

repeating-linear-gradient( 45deg, hsla(0, 0%, 100%, 0.3), hsla(0, 0%, 100%, 0.3) 20px, transparent 0, transparent 60px ), repeating-linear-gradient( -45deg, hsla(0, 0%, 100%, 0.3), hsla(0, 0%, 100%, 0.3) 20px, transparent 0, transparent 60px )

filter.dark: drop-shadow(0px 0px 1px var(--color-base-60)) drop-shadow(0px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4)) drop-shadow(0px 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4))
